, \"from\": 379, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"the vertigothat\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094they\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"Not just becauseBiles\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 488}, {\"ngram\": \"the session\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009ctwisties\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"the condition\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also a more elementary reason.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re getting mattress toppers today,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says coach C\\u00c3\\u00a9cile Landi.\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"There\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s also a more elementary reason\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"mattress toppers\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"coach C\\u00c3\\u00a9cile\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHallelujah!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The 13 athletes (five women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s artistic gymnasts, five men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s artistic gymnasts, two trampoline athletes and one rhythmic gymnast) arrived at the Olympic Village north of Paris on Monday.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 926, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.144373020435759e-18, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 951, \"end\": 956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1141543827757578e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 13 athletes\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"five women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s artistic gymnasts\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"five men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic gymnasts\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"two trampoline athletes\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"one rhythmic gymnast\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took about 15 seconds for them to notice a problem: The mattresses felt like rocks.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI sat on it and I was like, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Oh my God,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Landi with a laugh.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 15 seconds\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"The mattresses\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"rocks\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1107}, {\"ngram\": \"Landi\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"a laugh\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was like, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Mary [McDaniel, who runs logistics]!\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"[McDaniel\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"logistics\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Help!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Help was already on the way.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1189, \"end\": 11