508}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So far, the cardboard seems to have held up.\\u00c2 And the athletes are thrilled to have a real village experience, after a Tokyo Olympics marred by isolation.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cardboard\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"a real village experience\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"a Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"isolation\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gymnastics team stayed in a hotel in an attempt to mitigate the risks; this time around, they are enjoying even such details as the option to grab a snack.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The U.S. women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gymnastics team\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"a hotel\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2809}, {\"ngram\": \"an attempt\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"the risks\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"even such details\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2900}, {\"ngram\": \"the option\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"a snack\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThey were sliding it under the door for us [in Tokyo],\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Graba recalls.\\u00c2 Landi is a bit less effusive: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe food is what it is,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Landi, who was born in Paris and grew up in Marseille.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3098, \"end\": 3103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999886313, \"rank\": 1.1141543827757578e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour